sequenceDiagram
  participant User
  participant Form as Form / Client
  participant Action as Server Action
  participant Auth as requireUser / requireOwnedCampaign
  participant DB as adminDb() / Firestore

  Note over User,DB: --- Standard DM write (e.g. create session, update NPC) ---
  User->>Form: Submit (e.g. update NPC notes)
  Form->>Action: Invoke server action (formData / input)
  Action->>Auth: requireUser()
  Auth->>Auth: getSessionUser() → cookie
  Auth-->>Action: user or redirect(/login)
  Action->>Auth: requireOwnedCampaign(campaignId)
  Auth->>DB: campaigns.doc(campaignId).get()
  Auth-->>Action: ownership OK or throw
  Action->>DB: add() / update() / batch writes
  DB-->>Action: ref / done
  Action->>User: redirect() or revalidatePath()

  Note over User,DB: --- Player joining a campaign (joinCampaign) ---
  User->>Form: Submit join form (/join/[campaignId])
  Form->>Action: joinCampaign(campaignId, token)
  Action->>Auth: requireUser()
  Auth-->>Action: user
  Action->>DB: campaigns.doc(campaignId).get()
  Action->>Action: Validate campaign.inviteToken == token
  Action->>DB: players.add({ playerUserId: uid, playerEmail })
  Action->>DB: campaigns.update({ playerUserIds: arrayUnion(uid) })
  Action->>User: redirect(/player/dashboard)
